To be fair this car started off as a good one,wasn't like half the crap-heaps out there,whoever owned it looked after it.
(would've started straight away if refitted the intercooler @ ecu),
but the few mods you did by updateing and uprating the fuel system has done world good.👍
Didnt it allready have new suspension?
and body work was in really good condition,.and all drive train (engine/gearbox/clutch /transfer box and diff was all in good condition ).
You should've fitted a modern turbo and fitted a front mount intercooler on it to get the best out it though 👍
